  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA78">
<l>iṭarār paṭuvā reḻuneñcē vēḻan</l>
<l>toṭarvāṉ koṭumutalai cūḻnta – paṭamuṭaiya</l>
<l>painnākap paḷḷiyāṉ pātamē kaitoḻutuṅ</l>
<l>koynnākap pūmpōtu koṇṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who are those that [still] suffer affliction? Rise, heart! We will worship</l>
<l>with [our] hands the feet of him with a hooded green snake as [his] bed</l>
<l>who aimed at the very cruel crocodile that clung to the bull elephant,</l>
<l>– taking buds of [freshly] plucked Nāka flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
